{{Quote|So you've been away, Senator Ami&mdash;ah&mdash;Padmé?''"<br />"''On Chandrila, yes. I wasn't due back for a few days yet, but there was an outbreak of Ralltiiri measles in the enclave where I was staying. Since there was nothing I could do to help, I came home.|[[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin Skywalker]] and [[Padmé Amidala/Legends|Padmé Amidala]]|<ref name="Stealth">''[[Clone Wars Gambit: Stealth]]''</ref>}}
'''Measles''' was a disease characterized by spotty rashes and fevers. [[Jal Te Gniev]] had it during the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]].

